i/%D7%A7%D7%A8%D7%9C%D7%A1_%D7%A4%D7%95%D7%99%D7%95%D7%9C">קרלס פויול</a> (<a title="קפטן" href="http://he.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D7%A7%D7%A4%D7%98%D7%9F">קפטן</a>)</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="text-align: left;">6</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;"><a title="ספרד" href="http://he.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D7%A1%D7%A4%D7%A8%D7%93"><img class="thumbborder" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9a/Flag_of_Spain.svg/22px-Flag_of_Spain.svg.png" alt="Flag of Spain.svg" width="22" height="15" /></a></td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">קשר</td>\n<td><a title="צ\'אבי" href="http://he.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D7%A6%27%D7%90%D7%91%D7%99">צ\'אבי</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="text-align: left;">7</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;"><a title="ספרד" href="http://he.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D7%A1%D7%A4%D7%A8%D7%93"><img class="thumbborder" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9a/Flag_of_Spain.svg/22px-Flag_of_Spain.svg.png" alt="Flag of Spain.svg" width="22" height="15" /></a></td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">חלוץ</td>\n<td><a title="דויד וייה" href="http://he.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D7%93%D7%95%D7%99%D7%93_%D7%95%D7%99%D7%99%D7%94">דויד וייה</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="text-align: left;">8</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;"><a title="ספרד" href="http://he.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D7%A1%D7%A4%D7%A8%D7%93"><img class="thumbborder" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/9/9a/Flag_of_Spain.svg/22px-Flag_of_Spain.svg.png" alt="Flag of Spain.svg" width="22" height="15" /></a></td>\n<td style="text-align: center;">קשר</td>\n<td><a title="אנדרס אינייסטה" href="http://he.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D7%90%D7%A0%D7%93%D7%A8%D7%A1_%D7%90%D7%99%D7%A0%D7%99%D7%99%D7%A1%D7%98%D7%94">אנדרס אינייסטה</a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style="text-align: left;">9</td>\n<td style="text-align: center;"><a title="צ\'ילה" href="http://he.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D7%A6%27%D7%99%D7%9C%D7%94"><img class="thumbborder" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/